  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink296-kilavi">iravukkuṟi varukiṉṟa talaimakaṟkut tōḻi yāṟṟāmai kūṟi maṟuttatu.</p>
        <p xml:lang="en"> 
          How the confidante refused, expressing [the heroine's] inability, to the hero who comes for the night-tryst.              
        </p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink296">
<l>koṭicci kākkum peruṅkura lēṉa</l>
<l>laṭukkaṉ maññai kavaru nāṭa</l>
<l>naṭunāṭ kaṅkulum varuti</l>
<l>kaṭumā tākki ṉaṟiyēṉ yāṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
        <l>O man from the land where peacocks on the mountainside</l>
        <l>seize the millet with large ears which the creeper-like girl guards—</l>
        <l>you would come even in the night, at midnight.</l>
        <l>I do not know if a cruel animal [might] attack.</l>
        
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
